desc: Rebalance Holistic Therapy. Treatments available include Aromatherapy, Reflexology, Reiki, Hopi Ear Candling, Nasya Nasal Treatment and Indian Head Massage. My treatment room is based in Dublin 16, easily reached from Dublin 6, Dublin 12, Dublin 14, Dublin 16, Dublin 18 and Dublin 24.

layout.text: I specialise in helping people sleep better, destress and rebalance their body through holistic therapy. Different therapies resonate with different people so I tailor each treatment to meet each individual's need, leaving you relaxed, calm and rejuvenated.
